Package burlap.behavior.singleagent.vfa

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DifferentiableStateActionValue
    An extension of ParametricScalarFunction.ParametricStateActionFunction that is differentiable.
    DifferentiableStateValue
    An extension of ParametricScalarFunction.ParametricStateFunction that that is differentiable.
    FeatureDatabase
    An interface for defining a database of state features that can be returned for any given input state or input state-action pair.
    FunctionGradient
    An interface for defining and querying the gradient of a function.
    ParametricScalarFunction
    An interface for defining a parametric function that outputs a scalar values (double).
    ParametricScalarFunction.ParametricStateActionFunction
    A parametric function that operations on state-actions
    ParametricScalarFunction.ParametricStateFunction
    A Parametric function that operates on states.
    StateToFeatureVectorGenerator
    Many functions approximation techniques require a fixed feature vector to work and in many cases, using abstract features from the state attributes is useful.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionFeaturesQuery
    A class that associates an action with a set of state features.
    FunctionGradient.PartialDerivative
    A class for storing a partial derivative.
    FunctionGradient.SparseGradient
    A sparse FunctionGradient that only explicitly stores the partial derivative for parameters with non-zero partial derivatives.
    StateFeature
    A class for associating a state feature identifier with a value of that state feature
